sequenceDiagram
    participant H as BrokerHeartbeatManager
    participant M as ControllerManager
    participant C as JRaft/DLedger Controller
    participant P as ControllerRequestProcessor
    participant R as Broker ReplicasManager
    participant A as AutoSwitchHAService
    participant N as NameServer

    H->>M: Broker inactive
    M->>C: getReplicaInfo
    M->>C: electMaster
    C->>C: 复制选举状态并生成新 Epoch
    C-->>M: 新 Master、SyncStateSet
    M->>R: NOTIFY_BROKER_ROLE_CHANGED
    R->>R: changeBrokerRole
    alt 当前 Broker 当选
        R->>A: changeToMaster
    else 当前 Broker 为从
        R->>A: changeToSlave
    end
    R->>N: 重新注册 Broker 路由
